Install Xcode Command Line Tool
----

1. From App Store, you can download and install Xcode for free.
1. Open Xcode and follow menu Xcode > Preferences.. > Downloads > Components > Command Line Tools 
1. Install Command Line Tools

Install RVM
----

```
\curl -L https://get.rvm.io | bash
```

ref: <https://rvm.io/rvm/install>

Install Ruby
----

```
rvm install 2.0
```

